#

Cobb Salad

15 min
$12
550 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick

Description

A fresh and vibrant salad packed with protein and flavor, perfect for a light meal or a side dish.

Ingredients

  • romaine lettuce: 2 cups, chopped
  • cooked chicken breast: 1 cup, diced
  • bacon: 4 slices, cooked and crumbled
  • hard-boiled eggs: 2, chopped
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • avocado: 1, diced
  • blue cheese: 1/2 cup, crumbled
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • red wine vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • dijon mustard: 1 teaspoon
